'''微礦'''(英文：'''WeMine''') 是一家位於[[香港|香港]]，針對[[即時通訊|即時通訊]]軟件（如[[WhatsApp|WhatsApp]]、[[Facebook|Facebook]]和[[微信|微信]]）[[營銷|營銷]]管理及應用開發的服務供應商。<ref>{{cite web 
|url=http://www.aimpact.com/article/zho/%E5%BE%AE%E7%A4%A6%E5%89%B5%E8%BE%A6%E4%BA%BA%E6%8C%87%E4%BC%81%E6%A5%AD%E9%96%8B%E8%A8%AD%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E8%B3%AC%E8%99%9F%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E9%80%86%E8%BD%89%E7%9A%84%E6%88%B0%E7%95%A5%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE-1463278041|title= 微礦創辦人指企業開設微信賬號是不可逆轉的戰略考慮|date= 2018-06-11|website= AIMPACT 鋒投|publisher= AIMPACT 鋒投|accessdate= 2020-12-17}}</ref>其[[人工智能|人工智能]][[客戶關係管理|客戶關係管理]]平臺專注於[[即時通訊|即時通訊]]軟件的數據收集及分析，透過其系統功能簡化操作流程，為用家減省人力成本。<ref>{{cite web|url= https://fortuneinsight.com/web/posts/484419/insight%EF%BC%9A%E5%91%BD%E4%B8%AD%E6%B3%A8%E5%AE%9A%E7%9A%84ai%E5%89%B5%E6%A5%AD%E5%AE%B6%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E9%9B%BB%E8%85%A6%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E5%B8%B6%E9%A0%98%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD/|title= Insight：命中注定的AI創業家，以電腦管理帶領香港智能世界 謝偉傑｜WeMine微礦聯合創辦人|last= Fung|first= |date= 2018-12-23|website= Fortune Insight|publisher= WAVE INSIGHT LIMITED|accessdate= 2020-12-17|quote= |archive-date= 2020-12-03|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20201203171824/https://fortuneinsight.com/web/posts/484419/insight%EF%BC%9A%E5%91%BD%E4%B8%AD%E6%B3%A8%E5%AE%9A%E7%9A%84ai%E5%89%B5%E6%A5%AD%E5%AE%B6%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E9%9B%BB%E8%85%A6%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E5%B8%B6%E9%A0%98%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD/|dead-url= no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url= http://paper.wenweipo.com/2018/06/12/MC1806120002.htm|title= 微礦：微信公眾號可助營銷|last= 丘|first= 曉陽|date= 2018-06-12|website= 文匯報|publisher= 香港大公文匯傳媒集團全媒體中心|accessdate= 2020-12-17|quote= |archive-date= 2020-02-13|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200213140315/http://paper.wenweipo.com/2018/06/12/MC1806120002.htm|dead-url= no}}</ref>

微礦創辦於2014年年末，並於次年正式成立公司。<ref>{{cite web |url= https://www.hkcd.com/content/2017-06/05/content_1051037.html|title= 微礦科技：把創業變成一場「有趣」的體驗|last= 王|first= 曉蕾|date= 2017-06-05|website= 香港商報|publisher= 香港商報有限公司|accessdate= 2020-12-17|quote=}}</ref>該公司早年專注於為客戶開立微信號及提供管理、開發服務。<ref name="#1">{{cite web|url= https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20170807/HV6WXHY3UWBGIH4Y6VOB6ZQFYY/|title= 港人幫人開微信號 半年回本「fb都想抄微信」|last= 程|first= 詩敏|date= 2017-08-07|website= 香港蘋果日報|publisher= AD Internet Limited|accessdate= 2020-12-17|quote= |archive-date= 2021-06-22|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210622151221/https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20170807/HV6WXHY3UWBGIH4Y6VOB6ZQFYY/|dead-url= yes}}</ref>2016年4月，微礦入選南山深港夢工場創新企業培育計劃，<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.itpromag.com/wemine-19800|title=軟實力是港企皇牌 香港創初WeMine北上發圍|website=IT Pro Magazine|access-date=2016-04-12|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160508035601/http://www.itpromag.com/wemine-19800|archivedate=2016-05-08}}</ref>同時亦為[[IBM|IBM]] SoftLayer 的 Catalyst 計劃成員之一。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://cw.com.hk/news/hk-startup-wemine-selected-nanshan-innovation-hub|title=HK startup WeMine selected for Nanshan innovation hub|website=Computerworld Hong Kong|access-date=2016-04-12|archive-date=2016-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160424204000/http://cw.com.hk/news/hk-startup-wemine-selected-nanshan-innovation-hub|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2017年，獲新加坡[[天使投資者|天使投資者]]注資，完成天使輪融資。<ref>{{cite web|url= http://startupbeat.hkej.com/?p=46319|title= 香港初創「微礦」獲新加坡天使投資者注資|last= |first= |date= 2017-06-15|website= StartupBeat|publisher= 信報|accessdate= 2020-12-18|quote= 「微礦 」(WeMine) 獲新加坡資深天使投資者注資近100萬港元，該公司開發微信外掛程式，例如建立活動管理系統，讓客戶在微信上處理參加者報名及報到、活動通知及會場消息更新等項目。|archive-date= 2017-09-26|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20170926065630/http://startupbeat.hkej.com/?p=46319|dead-url= no}}</ref><ref name="#1"/>

2019年，微礦於深圳市軟件產業基地開設第三家辦公室，並同時宣佈發行其同名[[人工智能|人工智能]][[客戶關係管理|客戶關係管理]]平臺。<ref>{{cite web|url= https://www.marketing-interactive.com/hk-martech-start-up-wemine-launches-crm-platform-opens-mainland-offices|title= HK MarTech start-up WeMine launches CRM platform, opens mainland offices|last= |first= |date= 2019-02-19|website= Marketing Magazine|publisher= Lighthouse Independent Media|accessdate= 2020-12-17|quote= |archive-date= 2020-08-14|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200814052201/https://www.marketing-interactive.com/hk-martech-start-up-wemine-launches-crm-platform-opens-mainland-offices|dead-url= no}}</ref>

目前，微礦是港漂圈的廣告代理。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.digitalmarket.asia/2015/08/wemine-becomes-exclusive-advtg-agent-of-gangpiaoquan-on-wechat/|title=WeMine becomes exclusive advtg agent of GangPiaoQuan on WeChat|last=|first=|date=2015-08-05|work=|access-date=|via=|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160425163433/http://www.digitalmarket.asia/2015/08/wemine-becomes-exclusive-advtg-agent-of-gangpiaoquan-on-wechat/|archivedate=2016-04-25}}</ref>

